North America and Europe are the leading regions in the global infrared spectrophotometer devices market, followed by Asia Pacific.

5. What are the major applications of infrared spectrophotometer devices?
The major applications of infrared spectrophotometer devices include pharmaceutical analysis, food and beverage testing, and environmental monitoring.

